author: ybaturina
message:
Fix usage of hermetic tar and xz tools on aarch64 machines.

The previous tool packages were built on the machine with GLIBC 2.34, which caused errors on the runners with GLIBC 2.31.

PiperOrigin-RevId: 816862897
